### Thought ###
To find the best-rated Thai restaurant in Urbana, IL that serves duck cuisine, I will use Google Maps. The process involves searching for Thai restaurants in Urbana, IL, filtering for high ratings, and checking if they serve duck dishes. I will then review customer comments to summarize positive and negative feedback. Finally, I will compile the summary in the Notes app.

### Plan ###
1. Open the Google Maps app.
2. Search for "Thai restaurants in Urbana, IL."
3. Filter the results by rating to identify the best-rated restaurants.
4. Check the menus or reviews of the top-rated restaurants to confirm if they serve duck dishes.
5. Read customer reviews for the selected restaurant(s) and summarize the positive and negative feedback.
6. Open the Notes app and compile the summary.

### Current Subgoal ###
Open the Google Maps app.
